Package: SSS
Type: Package
Title: SSS framework for nonlinear IV analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Haodong Tian
Maintainer: Haodong Tian <htian2@mgh.harvard.edu>
Description: The three 'S' layers (stratification, scalar-on-function/scalar regression, sum-of-single-effect) for studying nonlinear effect in instrumental variable analysis.
